      • completeAll

        void completeAll()
        Closes all communication channels (i.e. observers).

        Note: All observers will be completed but not unsubscribed. The notification channel will not be stopped.

      • completeAll

        void completeAll(SubscriptionType type)
        Closes all communication channels (i.e. observers) of a certain type.

        Note: All observers will be completed but not unsubscribed. The notification channel will not be stopped.

        Parameters:
        type - type of subscription to consider.

      • createObserver

        @Nullable
Observer<?> createObserver(SubscriptionType subscriptionType,
                                      FilterOptions filter,
                                      io.reactivex.BackpressureStrategy strategy,

                                      CallbackWithException<FilterOptions,MbedCloudException> actionOnUnsubscription,
                                      boolean notifyOtherObservers,
                                      Resource correspondingResource)
        Creates an observer and registers it.
        Parameters:
        subscriptionType - type of subscription to consider.
        filter - filter to apply.
        strategy - backpressure strategy to apply for underlying communication channel.
        actionOnSubscription - action to perform on subscription
        actionOnUnsubscription - action to perform on unsubscription
        notifyOtherObservers - specifies whether the observer should notify other observers when it receives a notification.
        correspondingResource - resource corresponding to this observer.
        Returns:
        newly created observer
